Pre-coding Python Flask App File/Folder structure for a cinema booking system app.

Root, templates, static, models, tests.

#1. Root Directory

- app.py
- config.py
- requirements.txt
- .env

#2. /templates Directory

- base.html
- index.html
- booking.html
- payment.html
- confirmation.html

#3. /static Directory

- main.css
- main.js
- images/

#4. /models Directory

- cinema.py
- movie.py
- customer.py
- booking.py
- payment.py

#5. /tests Directory

- cinema_test.py
- movie_test.py
- customer_test.py
- booking_test.py
- payment_test.py
